@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rhbidu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos((v2 * v1))
    v0 = ((v1 * (v1 + 0.46 - tmp + 0.35)) / 0.48)
    tmp = wp.sin(0.86)
    v0 = 0.60
    tmp = 0.55
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.exp(wp.abs(v1 + 0.82)))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.sin(0.56))
    v2 = (((v0 + 0.98 + v1 + 0.40) / v0) / 0.69)
    data[tid] = v0
